      Return
        Ident value [type=<unresolved> const=<none>]
  Func use diverging=true
    Body
      Return
        Call [type=i32 const=<none> decl=sum spec=sum]
          Ident sum [type=<unresolved> const=<none>]
          IntLiteral 1 [type=i32 const=1 constant]
